{
  "stem": "8892.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we always had to be-- inside, we felt proud, and we knew we were better, special, because, you know, it's-- it's a different type of Gentile.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's mostly farmers, really.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the merchant in town, all of them, I think back, were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we had to sell them everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the farmers, all of them Gentiles.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when they were coming up and things changing, and they benefited by life, and we were going down, it was very hard.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were keeping the Jews down in every sense, every sense.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we had a certain amount of fear always that they shouldn't harm us or hurt us or anything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when it began to get worse is that we heard more and more stories.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, the newspaper would come to town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father was glued to it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But as a child, I didn't pay too much attention, because the life was the same routine still.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I knew they used to discuss it Saturdays, and-- and they used to talk about it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, of course, 1940, he had a brother in Czechoslovakia, which one part was actually, beginning was, I think, Hungary when he moved there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was very wealthy, and somehow word came that a [INAUDIBLE] started.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he wanted to save his two children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my brother was about 18, what was 17?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He would meet-- the oldest brother would meet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father, you know, told him, you go to the border, which was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a border of Czechoslovakia, and they would try to escape to Hungary, which I heard quite a few people, they thought, you know, the [INAUDIBLE] will not come to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They'll be safe.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
